reviewText: it's an amateurish recording of a 1 hour free seminar. Steve skims over a handful of candlestick symbols, glosses over how to correlate candlesticks with western analysis, then spends the rest of the hour promoting his site, DVD's and newsletter. This DVD is so far from instructional quality that I hesitate to give it even 1 star. That'll teach me to buy anything that doesn't have any reviews.
